ImageDescription{<7}ImportanceOfBuddhism
89	Monks are an integral part of Buddhism in Thailand ,
90	and Thai men are generally expected to spend a certain amount of time
91	living as a monk
92	at least once in their lifetime .
ImportanceOfBuddhism{=6}MonksAndWomen
93	Buddhist monks are meant to avoid sexual temptations ,
94	and in particular they do not touch women
95	or take things from women 's hands .
MonksAvoidContactingWomen{=5}WomenExpectations
96	Women should make every effort to make way for monks on the street and give them room
97	so they do not have to make contact with you .
98	Women should avoid offering anything to a monk with their hands .
WomenAvoidContactingMonks{<6}AppropriateWayForInteraction
99	Objects or donations should be placed in front of a monk
100	so he can pick it up ,
101	or place it on a special cloth
102	he carries with him .
AppropriateWayForDonation{>7}MonkAccompaniment
103	Monks will sometimes be aided by a layman
104	who will accept things from women merit-makers on their behalf .
MonksAndWomen{=4}AppropriateDonationTypes
105	Theravada Buddhist monks are also supposed to avoid material temptations
106	and as such , are not allowed to touch money ,
107	so offering money to a monk is considered to be a sign of disrespect in most Theravada Buddhist cultures .
TheravadaViewsOnMaterialTemptations{<5}AppropriateDonations
108	Therefore ,
109	should you wish to donate to a monk ,
110	you should only offer food , and put your monetary donation in the appropriate donation box at the temple .
AppropriateDonations{>6}FakeMonks
111	Those monks
112	that accept money
113	are almost always fakes .